videos.description: Wildcats' Phil Booth, Mikal Bridges, and Eric Paschall throw down the hammer in the first half.
videos.headline: Villanova's highlight reel of dunks

videos.description: Villanova's Omari Spellman denies a layup by Nicholls' Zaquavian Smith.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Spellman with a great block

videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall makes his second dunk of the night.
videos.headline: Paschall dunks off of nice spin move

videos.description: Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree slams it in for another Wildcats' dunk.
videos.headline: Cosby-Roundtree drops a hammer

videos.description: Wildcats' Phil Booth makes great use of the glass on a driving layup.
videos.headline: Booth penetrates for lay-in

videos.description: Villanova's Donte DiVincenzo receives a long pass for a breakaway run, and jams it in.
videos.headline: Wildcats' DiVincenzo posterizes defender

videos.description: Phil Booth with the takeaway, and lobs it to Mikal Bridges for a wide open dunk.
videos.headline: Two-handed jam by Wildcats' Bridges

videos.description: Two dunks by Dhamir Cosby-Roundtree close out a blowout win over Nicholls 113-77.
videos.headline: Villanova ends game with two dunks
